<h3>define :</h3>
<p>spread of diseases among humans + animals + plants . May be SLOW onset - HIV (because of intensity + spread)&nbsp;</p>
<h3>NEED for focus?&nbsp;</h3>
<ol>
<li>widespread + economy loss&nbsp;</li>
<li>globalisation&nbsp;</li>
<li>source of spread not known (mostly)</li>
<li>uncertainity + panic also&nbsp;</li>
<li>env degradation =&gt; man animal contact =&gt; more likely spread&nbsp;</li>
<li>growth of such weaponss - e.g ANthrax&nbsp;</li></ol>
<h3>used historically?&nbsp;</h3>
<ol>
<li>Bubonic plague&nbsp;</li>
<li>Germany in WWII - glanders</li></ol>
<h3>Legal framework?</h3>
<ol>
<li>Health = center + state list&nbsp;</li>
<li>EDA, 1897 (not sufficiently empower) + DMA 2005&nbsp;</li>
<li>BWC&nbsp;</li>
<li>Section 188 IPC = punish defaulter who disobey public order.</li></ol>
